				</a>
				<a href="/portfolio/flow-coffee-operations-agent" class="cs-card">
					<div class="cs-thumb"><img src="/images/flow_ops_bot_1x.webp" alt="Operations Agent" loading="lazy" /></div>
					<div class="cs-body">
						<span class="cs-tag">AI Agent</span>
						<h3>Operations Agent</h3>
						<p>Anomaly detection, forecasting, and KPI tracking across all machines.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="cs-foot"><span>Flow Coffee</span><span class="cs-arrow">→</span></div>
				</a>
